I can't do it...

44
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:13,375
I can't...

45
00:03:13,458 --> 00:03:15,125
Just hurry up...

46
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:16,291
kill me.

47
00:03:16,375 --> 00:03:17,750
You have to stay with me...!

48
00:03:17,833 --> 00:03:19,583
There's still a chance
you can revert...!

49
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:21,041
Don't give up!

50
00:03:21,125 --> 00:03:22,541
Revert!

51
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,125
