for a second.

76
00:06:12,583 --> 00:06:14,666
And just when I thought
you were about to awaken

77
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:17,208
you found a way
to fight it off somehow.

78
00:06:17,291 --> 00:06:18,666
I suppose that's
one of the perks

79
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:21,125
with being so
highly ranked, huh...?

80
00:06:21,208 --> 00:06:24,416
