nothing short of brilliant.

81
00:06:26,625 --> 00:06:27,791
Well enough talk.

82
00:06:27,875 --> 00:06:31,291
It's time you were
awakened, don't you think?

83
00:06:31,375 --> 00:06:33,541
Take care of it for me,
will you Dauf?

84
00:06:37,333 --> 00:06:38,916
