112
00:07:57,541 --> 00:07:59,708
So, what now?

113
00:07:59,791 --> 00:08:01,208
Hold nothing back!!

114
00:08:20,291 --> 00:08:23,333
Owwww!

115
00:08:23,416 --> 00:08:25,083
Fascinating.

116
00:08:33,208 --> 00:08:36,333
Attacking from opposite
directions ruins Dauf's focus...

117
00:08:36,416 --> 00:08:39,333
