Nineteen.

125
00:09:05,625 --> 00:09:06,958
Twenty.

126
00:09:09,625 --> 00:09:11,083
Twenty-one!

127
00:09:13,875 --> 00:09:15,250
Maximum...

128
00:09:15,333 --> 00:09:17,666
