234
00:15:01,041 --> 00:15:02,583
Now's our chance
to end this...!

235
00:15:02,666 --> 00:15:05,583
Drive your GreatSword into
that monster's throat!

236
00:15:06,958 --> 00:15:07,750
Idiot...!

237
00:15:07,833 --> 00:15:09,708
Prepare to be crushed!

238
00:15:10,833 --> 00:15:12,833
I need to focus...

239
00:15:16,291 --> 00:15:18,583
Read his Yoki aura so
that my Quick Sword

240
00:15:18,666 --> 00:15:21,000
