241
00:15:22,333 --> 00:15:23,833
What's that?

242
00:15:37,083 --> 00:15:39,000
Impossible...!

243
00:15:39,083 --> 00:15:41,958
Her right arm is under
her complete control...

244
00:15:42,041 --> 00:15:44,083
Somehow she's
able to attack...

245
00:15:44,166 --> 00:15:46,750
