really be afraid of.

276
00:17:58,916 --> 00:17:59,958
Okay then...

277
00:18:00,041 --> 00:18:01,625
Fair is fair, right...?

278
00:18:01,708 --> 00:18:05,291
All three of you have sacrificed
too much to get this far.

279
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:11,708
The man that you seek...

280
00:18:11,791 --> 00:18:15,041
Is in the northern
territory of Alfons.

281
00:18:15,125 --> 00:18:18,416
There in a land
frozen in ice.

282
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:21,416
You will find the
Silver King Isley.

283
00:18:24,083 --> 00:18:25,375
Silver King Isley...

284
00:18:25,458 --> 00:18:27,291
In the land of Alfons...

285
00:18:27,375 --> 00:18:29,583
It's worse than I expected.

286
00:18:29,666 --> 00:18:32,250
If you want to
consider defeating him...

287
00:18:32,333 --> 00:18:34,708
then you must join me...

288
00:18:34,791 --> 00:18:36,875
It's the only way.

289
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:41,291
Well then Warriors...

290
00:18:41,375 --> 00:18:43,375
We shall meet again.

291
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:50,250
How could she...

292
00:18:50,333 --> 00:18:52,375
just disappear...

293
00:18:52,458 --> 00:18:54,041
so quickly?

294
00:18:56,416 --> 00:18:58,250
Damn it...

295
00:18:58,333 --> 00:19:00,083
I never imagined the
Creatures of the Abyss

296
00:19:00,166 --> 00:19:02,500
would be so
incredibly powerful.

297
00:19:04,541 --> 00:19:05,875
And look at me...

298
00:19:05,958 --> 00:19:08,958
My abilities are pathetic
compared to those things.

299
00:19:14,708 --> 00:19:15,458
Well now...

300
00:19:15,541 --> 00:19:17,041
That's done...

301
00:19:17,125 --> 00:19:19,875
and I must return to
my original objective.

302
00:19:22,791 --> 00:19:24,625
Number Forty-Seven...

303
00:19:24,708 --> 00:19:26,458
I have been given the
task of returning you

304
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:28,208
to the Organization.

305
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:33,250
If you follow me quietly then
we won't have a problem...

306
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:35,166
You know what will happen...

307
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:38,125
if you oppose me.

308
00:19:38,208 --> 00:19:40,875
I have no intention of going
back to the Organization.

309
00:19:40,958 --> 00:19:42,416
Not right now...

310
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:44,208
There's something I need to do
first that's more important

311
00:19:44,291 --> 00:19:45,750
than your task.

312
00:19:45,833 --> 00:19:47,375
So in other words...

313
00:19:47,458 --> 00:19:51,125
you would rather launch yourself
into another battle right now...

314
00:19:51,208 --> 00:19:53,750
And end the day as a corpse.

315
00:20:00,625 --> 00:20:01,416
Jean...

316
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,750
What do you think you're doing?

317
00:20:02,833 --> 00:20:05,000
Trust me this isn't the
way I wanted it to happen

318
00:20:05,083 --> 00:20:06,958
but she saved my
life back there...

319
00:20:07,041 --> 00:20:09,583
I gave her my word that my
life now belongs to her

320
00:20:09,666 --> 00:20:11,333
and I intend to keep it.

321
00:20:12,958 --> 00:20:16,208
You know by doing this you
are defying the Organization.

322
00:20:16,291 --> 00:20:18,958
I've already lost
my life once before...

323
00:20:19,041 --> 00:20:21,083
so the last thing I'll do
is compromise my honor

324
00:20:21,166 --> 00:20:22,833
to extend my time.

325
00:20:43,791 --> 00:20:46,666
Fighters of such a low rank
have zero chance of surviving

326
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:49,000
a skirmish with a
Creature of the Abyss.

327
00:20:49,083 --> 00:20:50,541
It would be suicide.

328
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,166
And after the creature
pulverizes your bodies

329
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:57,166
into millions of tiny pieces,
any chance of finding you

330
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:58,583
will be slim.

331
00:20:58,666 --> 00:21:01,541
In fact it'd be an impossible
job not worth taking on.

332
00:21:03,375 --> 00:21:05,791
The next time we cross paths
it is anyone's guess if

333
00:21:05,875 --> 00:21:08,333
I will embrace you
or strike you down...

334
00:21:08,416 --> 00:21:10,125
Until then I hope
you both survive

335
00:21:10,208 --> 00:21:12,583
and the best of luck
to you, you'll need it.

336
00:21:22,291 --> 00:21:23,666
Stand fast!

337
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,458
I said hold your positions!

338
00:21:25,541 --> 00:21:26,250
Eva!

339
00:21:26,333 --> 00:21:27,083
Kate's gone!

340
00:21:27,166 --> 00:21:29,625
They got her!

341
00:21:29,708 --> 00:21:31,583
Lucia!

342
00:22:48,041 --> 00:22:50,708
A chance encounter,
and another conspiracy...

343
00:22:50,791 --> 00:22:52,958
Signs of a storm lie ahead.

344
00:22:53,041 --> 00:22:55,833
Next time, The Carnage
in the North, Part One.

